	<div class="commentbody">
      <p>Does not work for HTML (WP 3.7.1) for me.</p>
<p>E.g.:<br />
[code start]<br />
<code><br />
Homepage<br />
</code><br />
[/code end]</p>
<p>Result: "Homepage" as a link:<br />
<em>Homepage</em></p>
<p>Even code lang="html" or pre lang="html" does not work either.</p>
<p>The WYSIWYG Editor converts the markup always.</p>
<p>PS: Otherwise other languages work like a charm.<br />
PPS: I am curios whether the code above is displayed correctly or rendered.</p>

      <div class="reply">
