	<div class="commentbody">
      <p>As I see, the code of my previous post is rendered. I replaced tag signs &#8220;&lt;&gt;&#8221; with &#8220;[]&#8221; and show it below again:</p>
<p>[pre][code markup="none"]<br />
[html][font color=blue][u]Homepage[/u][/font][html]<br />
[/code][/pre]</p>
<p>Result: &#8220;Homepage&#8221; as a link:<br />
Homepage</p>

